<title>MONACO: TENNIS-MONTE CARLO OPEN FIRST ROUND RESULTS.</title>
<headline>TENNIS-MONTE CARLO OPEN FIRST ROUND RESULTS.</headline>
<dateline>MONTE CARLO 1997-04-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>First round results in the</p>
<p>$2,300,000 Monte Carlo men's Open tennis tournament on Monday</p>
<p>(prefix number denotes seeding):</p>
<p>16-Sergi Bruguera (Spain) beat Javier Sanchez (Spain) 6-4 6-1</p>
<p>  Magnus Larsson (Sweden) beat Hicham Arazi (Morocco) 6-3 6-3</p>
<p>Christian Ruud (Norway) beat Sjeng Schalken (Netherlands) 6-4 6-2</p>
<p>Slava Dosedel (Czech Republic) beat Gustavo Kuerten (Brazil) 6-1 3-6 6-1</p>
<p>Fabrice Santoro (France) beat Francisco Roig (Spain) 6-4 6-1</p>
<p>13-Jim Courier (U.S.) beat Dominik Hrbaty (Slovakia) 6-7 (1-7) 7-5 6-4</p>
<p>Emilio Alvarez (Spain) beat Karim Alami (Morocco) 6-3 3-6 6-0</p>
<p>Arnaud Boetsch (France) beat Davide Sanguinetti (Italy) 6-2 6-7</p>
<p>(6-8) 6-4</p>
<p>Bohdan Ulihrach (Czech Republic) beat Magnus Gustafsson</p>
<p>(Sweden) 7-6 (7-2) 6-2</p>
<p>Carlos Costa (Spain) beat Karol Kucera (Slovakia) 6-2 6-7 (6-8)</p>
<p>6-4</p>
<p>Cedric Pioline (France) beat Omar Camporese (Italy) 6-3 6-4</p>
</text>
